WEBVTT

00:04:29.320 --> 00:04:32.240
mavjudligiga ishora qilmoqda.

00:04:33.160 --> 00:04:37.776
Ular o'zgalarning tuyg'ulariga loqaydmas,

00:04:37.800 --> 00:04:41.576
balki iztirobli holatiga sovuqqonlik 
bilan qarashadi

00:04:41.600 --> 00:04:42.816
Va ayniqsa, ular yuzdagi

00:04:42.840 --> 00:04:46.736
bunday qo’rquv ifodalarini 
ajratishda qiynalishadi

00:04:46.760 --> 00:04:50.456
qo’rquv ifodalari esa hissiy 
iztirobni yetkazadi

00:04:50.480 --> 00:04:53.096
hamda buni ko’rgan kishilarda odamiylik va

00:04:53.120 --> 00:04:54.376
ko'mak istagini uyg’otadi,

00:04:54.400 --> 00:04:57.096
odamiyligi zaif kishilarning bunday

00:04:57.120 --> 00:04:59.240
alomatga beparvo bo'lish moyilligi ham bor